      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "7. failed payments\nfailure/ mismatch from reconciliation can happen at any stage PSP, intenal systems\nwe classify failure in to buckets",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "7. failed payments\nfailure/ mismatch from reconciliation can happen at any stage PSP, intenal systems\nwe classify failure in to buckets",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QP6Xb2-WT6RNgBNHI2aWK",
